headline: Tractor Supply (NasdaqGS:TSCO) Expands Into Pet Pharmacy With Launch Of Tractor Supply Rx
summary: Tractor Supply (NasdaqGS:TSCO) recently announced the launch of Tractor Supply Rx, an innovative pharmacy service for pets and animals, which enhances its customer offerings. Despite this positive development, the company's share price declined by 4% over the last week, in line with broader market trends. The market generally experienced a 1% decline during this period driven by continued tariff concerns and uncertainty surrounding Federal Reserve leadership. Tractor Supply's latest venture...

headline: Tractor Supply Launches New Tractor Supply Rx With Easy Ordering for Pet and Animal Pharmacy Needs
summary: BRENTWOOD, Tenn., April 21, 2025--Tractor Supply Company (NASDAQ: TSCO), the largest rural lifestyle retailer in the United States, announced today the launch of Tractor Supply Rx, the Company’s convenient and low-cost pet and animal pharmacy offering.
